name: Rare Scups
description: The Rare Scups' bioluminescent spurs are perfectly suited to its predominantly noctural [sic] lifestyle. Sure, it performs along nonchalantly during the day, but it's total mystery what it does after the sun sets. Every once in a while, a company of ambitious Monsters will resolve to stay up long enough to witness a Rare Scups in nighttime action, but the siren song of the Castle's beds always proves too much to resist.
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 15 hr 30 min, Enahnced Time: 11 hr 37 min 30 sec
